name: Steve Lacy
bio: 🎶 I make my living on the evening news 🎶        5 & 10PM ⚓ at Fox5 in NYC.

social_posts.post_text: Breaking News - it’s the most wonderful time of the year again. @natasha_verma
Merry Christmas and Happy Holidays to everyone!
Love them Phish. Oh yeah!

I cant believe it, but today marks my 10th anniversary as 10PM Anchor here at Fox 5! Many thanks to all my colleagues, bosses and all the viewers who tune in nightly. I never take for granted how lucky I am to occupy this chair and call the greatest city on earth home. 
📸 @natasha_verma
Fun promo shoot day in Times Square! Thanks to our amazing creative team for all their hard work. Much more to come from them soon. In the meantime, here’s a little behind-the-scenes from yesterday.
It’s (a bus ad for the) 10PM, do you know where your children are?

Excited to have one of my sports card pieces up for auction in this weekend’s @gcdstigers annual #TigerBash fundraiser. Even more exciting is that this 30” x 40” screenprint on canvas of a 2017 Flawless Donovan Mitchell 1/1 Rookie Patch Auto is signed by Donovan Mitchell himself! Here’s a quick look at how I made this piece. Please share with any sports card enthusiasts looking for a truly unique addition to their collection.
Happy Mother’s Day to the best Mother ever, who always puts our threenager’s needs above her own! Love you two.
She wasnt really feeling pictures with her Dad today, which is her prerogative as a 3 year old! Had a great Father’s Day nonetheless.
It’s called Americana, folks. 🇺🇸
Captain Vacation.
Anna’s *first ever* night away from our beloved Autumn since her birth in April 2020 (🤯) was a rousing success. I feel like that must be some sort of world record? #MotherOfTheMillenium
null
Best band. Best fans. Best city. A million new best friends. Finally hit show 100 (in case you haden’t heard). 🤣 No theme. No shaving!! Until we do it again. ⭕️
First Day of Preschool! So proud of both my ladies who handled the (temporary) separation beautifully. Only an hour til pickup!

Here’s a quick look at my booth from last week’s @superfineartfair in NYC. Thanks to everyone from Superfine for pulling off a truly outstanding 4-day event in the heart of Manhattan. Thanks to my rock n’ roll brother @markweissguy for trusting me with his legendary images and always believing in my vision for our collaboration, my wife @annagilligan for allowing me the endless time needed to pursue my passion for screenprinting and all my amazing fellow artists who were brave enough to share their work with the world. I learned so much from everyone I had the pleasure of talking to.
It’s Autumn Bus Ad Season again! 🍂🍁
Family affair today cheering on @natasha_verma as she finished her first #nycmarathon!!! Story at 10… on Tuesday (after a day of rest)!
Wishing you all a safe, happy and healthy Holiday Season! If it looks like we’re having fun it’s because we are! Thank you all so much from all of us at Fox 5.
Wishing you all a Merry Christmas and Happy New Year.
Home for the Holidays. Teaching Autumn the classics!
A Phish NYE for the ages. #Multibeast
